    <main>
        <section class="carousell">
            <div class="img-list" id="img-list">
                <img src="~/BIBTour/Assets/images/AnadoluKulturGezileri.jpg"
                     width="1000" />

                <img src="~/BIBTour/Assets/images/Hero-interest-people.jpg"
                     width="1000" />
                <img src="~/BIBTour/Assets/images/cultural-tour.jpg" width="1000" />
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <h2>Culture Tours</h2>
                    <p>
                        Traveling is one of the most fascinating ways to explore different
                        cultures and witness them first-hand. Cultural tours offer an
                        excellent option for those who want to live these exciting
                        experiences. Cultural tours designed to explore a country's
                        history, traditions, art and lifestyle offer travelers the
                        opportunity to create unforgettable memories.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-section">
                <div class="caro-btn" onclick="slideImg(0)"></div>
                <div class="caro-btn" onclick="slideImg(1)"></div>
                <div class="caro-btn" onclick="slideImg(2)"></div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <script src="~/BIBTour/Pages/CampOtels.js"></script>
    </main>
    <div class="hotel-body">
        <h1><div class="head">Culture Tours</div></h1>
        <div class="head"></div>

        <div class="otel-card">
            <figure class="cardO">
                <div class="card-hero">
                    <img class="card-img"
                         src="~/BIBTour/Assets/images/ottomantour.jpg"
                         alt="" />
                    <div class="card-middle">
                        <p class="card-middle-text">Istanbul Ottoman Empire Tour</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h5 class="card-price">$169/pp</h5>
                        <p class="card-address">
                            Step back in time with our Istanbul Ottoman Empire Tour, a
                            private exploration of the rich heritage of the Ottoman Empire
                            that resides in the city! Whether you're fascinated by the deep
                            history or you want some interesting and stunning places for
                            some photographs, this is the private Istanbul tour for you!
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-details">
                            5 nights 6 days &middot; Transportation by Plane &middot; Visa
                            Free
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1%; padding: 1%" class="card-buttons">
                        <a href="@Url.Action("LogIn", "User")"
                           class="card-btnn"
                           style="background-color: rgb(54, 50, 162)">Proceed to Payment</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-buttons">
                        <a href="~/BIBTour/Pages/Tours/IstanbulOttomanTour.html" class="card-btnn">View More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="otel-card">
            <figure class="cardO">
                <div class="card-hero">
                    <img class="card-img"
                         src="~/BIBTour/Assets/images/culturetours_taiwan.jpg"
                         alt="" />
                    <div class="card-middle">
                        <p class="card-middle-text">A Taste Of Taiwan By Train</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h5 class="card-price">$139/pp</h5>
                        <p class="card-address">
                            Taiwan tour offers you the opportunity to discover this
                            mysterious island known as the pearl of Asia. When your tour
                            begins, you will marvel at Taipei's modern skyline and navigate
                            a world of skyscrapers tall like Taipei 101. However, a tour to
                            Taiwan gives you the chance to discover not only modernity but
                            also the mysteries of this island, which has a rich historical
                            and cultural heritage.
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-details">
                            7 nights 8 days &middot; Transportation by Bus &middot; With
                            Visa
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1%; padding: 1%" class="card-buttons">
                        <a href="@Url.Action("LogIn", "User")"
                           class="card-btnn"
                           style="background-color: rgb(54, 50, 162)">Proceed to Payment</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-buttons">
                        <a href="~/BIBTour/Pages/Tours/TaiwanTour.html" class="card-btnn">View More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="otel-card">
            <figure class="cardO">
                <div class="card-hero">
                    <img class="card-img"
                         src="~/BIBTour/Assets/images/moroccotour.jpg"
                         alt="" />
                    <div class="card-middle">
                        <p class="card-middle-text">Epic Morocco Tour</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h5 class="card-price">$129/pp</h5>
                        <p class="card-address">
                            Are you ready to discover the mystical beauties of Morocco? The
                            Morocco tour takes you on a fascinating journey, starting from
                            the lively souks of Marrakech, through traditional towns and the
                            Sahara Desert.
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-details">
                            2 Weeks &middot; Transportation by Plane &middot; With Visa
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1%; padding: 1%" class="card-buttons">
