                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-info">
                        <h5 class="card-price">$219/pp</h5>
                        <p class="card-address">
                            Mexico tour takes you to the colorful culture and natural
                            beauties of Mexico. Filled with historical riches, magnificent
                            beaches and lively festivals, this short journey offers you the
                            unique charm of Mexico.
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-details">
                            1 Month &middot; Transportation by Bus &middot; Visa Free
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1%; padding: 1%" class="card-buttons">
                        <a href="@Url.Action("LogIn", "User")"
                           class="card-btnn"
